unittitle_ssm: Joyce Wheeler American Federation of Teachers Papers
abstract_ssm: Joyce Wheeler was a member of the American Federation of Teachers (AFT). She was particularly active in the United Action Caucus, a rank and file organization within the AFT. Wheeler was also a participant in Local 340 of the AFT, known as the Baltimore Teachers Union (BTU), and in BTU's Teacher Unity Caucus. The collection consists of correspondence, newsletters, constitutions and other governing documents, convention resolutions and proceedings, flyers, and other materials collected and produced by a variety of teachers' organizations, especially the AFT and the United Action Caucus, AFT.
